data.description:
Welcome to this stunning house that seamlessly combines elegance and comfort. As you step inside, your feet are greeted by the inviting touch of hardwood floors and new carpet throughout creating a warm atmosphere. The living room becomes the heart of the home, boasting a fireplace that adds both character and warmth to the space. Adjacent to the living room is a kitchen, featuring a large center island for food prep and a cozy eat-in area bathed in natural light streaming through expansive windows. A walkout feature allows for seamless access to the outdoors, where a spacious deck awaits. For more formal occasions, there is a separate dining room, providing a setting for memorable gatherings. Home has main floor laundry for convenience.
Descend to the newly finished lower level, and you'll discover a sprawling family room that offers endless possibilities for relaxation and entertainment. Enjoy walking/biking trails with neighborhood access to Woodland Trails Regional Park.
